{"tid":1580840,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[不分和勇] 召喚所有自問創意無限既巴絲","createTime":"2019-09-19T09:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T04:49:50.000Z","uid":24178,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"462c238d4344ebafc0f56f4b8e36a42483c09fb8","tid":1580840,"uid":24178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:18:46.000Z","msg":"自反送中運動開始到依家既民主運動已經三個月<br />\n一路以來無論和理非定勇武兄弟都展現左極大創意<br />\n但隨住政府拖字訣 運動好似久不久就進入膠著狀態或者會變左被對家帶住來行<br />\n<br />\n我想大家可以將自己諗過既一啲抗爭手法係呢到講出來<br />\n無論幾on9 都好 好多時一啲好既idea 就係鳩下鳩下先諗到出來 (當初airdrop 都係講下笑 笑下笑下就成左依加其中一招主力)<br />\n<br />\n自己無original idea 既就碌下post 見到好既就幫手改進或者upvote<br />\n行動既兄弟得閒就跟熱門回覆排望下 講出前線既concern<br />\n<br />\nBe water <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好俾一時既成功困住自己 </span><br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"658d4590bca8905eae976428f26b785a21bc5e28","tid":1580840,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T09:19:46.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[公海 文宣 行動整合] 9.29全球抗赤納粹集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579667</a><br />\n全世界一齊對準ChiNazi極權！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BZiskWr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBZiskWr.png&h=b85bf973&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5faDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=ec06c932\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global AntiChiNazi 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5faDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D